Steps to build & run project:

1. Go to root project root directory i,e. "atm".
2. Make sure maven and JDK 8 or higher version installed in the system.
3. Execute the maven command in root directory "mvn clean package".
4. Jar atm-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar will be created in target folder.
5. Run the run file & cmd is "java -jar atm-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar"
6. SpringBoot application will be app and running.

Test the APIS::
1. Open the browser
2. To get list of atms, hit the below url : http://localhost:8080/api/atms/
3. To filter of atms by city, hit the below url : http://localhost:8080/api/atms/{cityName}

Docker Build:

1. mvn clean package -DskipTests=true
2. docker-compose -f docker/docker-compose.yml build --no-cache
3. docker-compose -f docker/docker-compose.yml up -d


